readme:
#language-fs-ionide

language-fs-ionide is just a quick package for syntax highlighting for F#, using the grammars provided by [Ionide](http://ionide.io).  I did not write any of this code, I only separated the grammars into their own package, for those who want to simply edit F# code without using an IDE.
